## RISK ASSESSMENT

### Implementation Risks

#### HIGH RISK
- **Technical Complexity**: Analytics domain requires advanced time-series processing
- **Integration Complexity**: Cross-cutting concerns affect all existing domains
- **Performance Impact**: Additional resources may affect query performance

#### MEDIUM RISK  
- **Resource Allocation**: Requires significant development investment
- **Customer Expectations**: Existing customers may expect immediate access
- **Market Timing**: Competitive pressure to deliver quickly

#### LOW RISK
- **Technical Foundation**: Solid Ash framework foundation supports expansion
- **Architecture**: Multi-tenant design accommodates new domains well
- **Team Capability**: Proven ability to implement complex domains

### Mitigation Strategies

#### Technical Risk Mitigation
- Incremental domain implementation with feature flags
- Performance testing at each phase
- Backward compatibility maintenance

#### Business Risk Mitigation  
- Customer communication about roadmap
- Phased rollout with beta customers
- Revenue protection through existing feature completeness

